INTRO                                             A tall slim fellow stands smiling in front of you. He shakes your hand.                                                                                                                                 NAME                                              "Hugh. Welcome to level two!"                                                                                                                                                                           JOB                                               "I keep all clean and never tire;                                                until the night, and then RETIRE."                                                                                     BYE                                               "And now our chat it is all done;                                                until one day, another one."                                                                                                                                             "On that my thoughts art rather slow; best ye try an' talk to Joe."                                                                                                                                     RETIRE                                            "'Tis my job to clean the floors, as well as many other chores."                                                                                                                                        WATER                                             "For that you must another hire, Speak to Trilla, ask of FIRE.                   When you go to gather sticks, you'll surely see her, dungeon six."                                                     FIRE                                              "That is what I said, oh friend. And now our chat has come to end."                                                                                                                                     